title.en: My food got cold. Serves me right.
title.es: I just sat down. Time to stand up.
title.pt-BR: The shift begins. Time to pretend.

comment.en: Their instincts for self-preservation seem far more reliable than my own, frankly.
comment.es: Parece que los suyos son más fiables que los míos.
comment.pt-BR: Eles se preservam melhor que eu, confesso.

title.pt-BR: My break started. What a joke.

comment.en: My survival strategy mainly involves hoping the copier still works tomorrow.
comment.es: Sobrevivo si la copiadora sigue viva mañana.
comment.pt-BR: Se a copiadora funcionar amanhã, já tá bom.
